    Aracnia nodded at Kitkat, "Its a good idea. Let him get scrapped for our 
cause. Its the Predacon way." She laughed. "So, should we bring him in and 
talk to him about it?"

    Megatron paced. The females hadnt called him back yet. What could take 
them so long? They were playing mind games with him, he knew they were. This 
psycological tourture had better be worth it....
    "Argh! How long will they take!" Megatron roared in anger. Hell Beast 
just shook his head with his diplomatic knowledge of how these types of 
meetings went.
    He sished, "Megatron, these things take time. I wouldnt be surprized if 
we didnt hear from them for another week." And then trotted off.
